h1(#wxtooltip). Wx::ToolTip

This class holds information about a tooltip associated with a window
(see "Window#set_tool_tip":window.html#Window_settooltip).

The two static methods, "ToolTip#enable":tooltip.html#ToolTip_enable and
"ToolTip#set_delay":tooltip.html#ToolTip_setdelay can be used to globally
alter tooltips behaviour.

